## Wilcoxon rank-sum test in R: with long data

Make data long (if it's not already long):


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
CPZdata_long <- CPZdata %>% 
  pivot_longer(cols = c(control,cap_CPZ), 
               names_to = "Group",
               values_to = "Current")

head(CPZdata_long)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
# A tibble: 6 Ã— 2
  Group   Current
  <chr>     <dbl>
1 control    3024
