```
:::
:::





Exact p-value

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
wilcox.test(Current ~ Group, 
            data = CPZdata_long, 
            alternative = c("two.sided"), 
            mu = 0, 
            exact = TRUE) %>% 
  tidy() %>% gt() 
```

